  31:verify.c      **** *
  32:verify.c      **** * Description: Copy len bytes from x to r if b is 1;
  33:verify.c      **** *              don't modify x if b is 0. Requires b to be in {0,1};
  34:verify.c      **** *              assumes two's complement representation of negative integers.
